name: GTEx Analysis Release V8
description: The GTEx v8 data set consists of 948 donors and 17,382 samples from 52 tissues and two cell lines, with 838 donors and 15,253 samples having both RNA sequence (RNA-seq) and genotype data from whole genome sequencing (WGS).

name: GTEx Biobank Samples
description: The GTEx samples in the freezers, not the ones used for analysis.

name: GTEx Histology Samples
description: GTEx samples used for histology imaging.
